npc1: Welcome. Before you head out, a few things.
npc1: Move with [A] and [D]. Jump with [Space] — tap it again in the air for a double jump.
npc1: Press [F] to talk to survivors out there. They know things you need to hear.
npc1: Keep an eye on your health bar — the creatures out there will wear you down.
npc1: The city ahead was corrupted by something deep inside the internet. You are the one who can trace it to the source.
npc1: First time here? I can walk you through everything — movement, skills, the traps — in a safe practice room.
- Yes, show me the tutorial
	npc1: Smart. Take your time in there.
	[signal arg="goto_tutorial"]
- No, I am ready
	npc1: Brave. Good luck out there.
